sql_query.sql: SELECT "django_admin_log"."id", "django_admin_log"."action_time", "django_admin_log"."user_id", "django_admin_log"."content_type_id", "django_admin_log"."object_id", "django_admin_log"."object_repr", "django_admin_log"."action_flag", "django_admin_log"."change_message", "api_user"."id", "api_user"."password", "api_user"."last_login", "api_user"."is_superuser", "api_user"."first_name", "api_user"."last_name", "api_user"."is_staff", "api_user"."is_active", "api_user"."date_joined", "api_user"."username", "api_user"."email", "django_content_type"."id", "django_content_type"."app_label", "django_content_type"."model" FROM "django_admin_log" INNER JOIN "api_user" ON ("django_admin_log"."user_id" = "api_user"."id") LEFT OUTER JOIN "django_content_type" ON ("django_admin_log"."content_type_id" = "django_content_type"."id") WHERE "django_admin_log"."user_id" = 1 ORDER BY "django_admin_log"."action_time" DESC LIMIT 6
